<bibRefCitation id="EFA64B68C049ED45BB28F8E09F9D211E" author="ASSING V" box="[324,509,1827,1855]" pageId="2" pageNumber="249" pagination="380 - 383" refId="ref8928" refString="ASSING V. (2012 a): Unterfamilie Paederinae FLEMING, 1821; pp. 322 - 369, 380 - 383. In: ASSING V. &amp; M. SCHULKE (eds), Freude-Harde-Lohse-Klausnitzer - Die Kafer Mitteleuropas. Band 4. Staphylinidae I. Zweite neubearbeitete Auflage. - Spektrum Akademischer Verlag, Heidelberg and Berlin: I-XII, 1 - 560." type="book chapter" year="2012">ASSING 2012a</bibRefCitation>
) and was recently reported also from East Siberia (
<bibRefCitation id="EFA64B68C049ED45BEE9F8E09B58211E" author="RYVKIN A" box="[1157,1336,1827,1855]" pageId="2" pageNumber="249" pagination="135 - 170" refId="ref9258" refString="RYVKIN A. B. (2011): On new and poorly known Lathrobium (s. str.) species from Siberia and the Russian Far East (Insecta: Coleoptera: Staphylinidae: Paederinae). - Baltic Journal of Coleopterology 11 (2): 135 - 170." type="journal article" year="2011">RYVKIN 2011</bibRefCitation>
).
</paragraph>
